text:
To live a full life, a
life without regrets.

One in which I stay
close to my core

values and do things
that I truly believe in.

One in which I push
my boundaries and I'm

not held back by fear
of failure or judgment.

One in which I speak up and be a
force for change when required.

I hope to be an
active participant

in shaping the world around me,
and not just a mere spectator.
